graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kueue -->|CRD management<br/>pod orchestration| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server 1.25+]
    Kueue -->|webhook TLS certs<br/>auto-rotation| CertManager[cert-manager 1.17+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Kueue -.->|TFJob, PyTorchJob<br/>MPIJob, etc.| KubeflowTraining[Kubeflow Training Operator 1.9+]
    Kueue -.->|RayJob<br/>RayCluster| RayOperator[Ray Operator 1.3+]
    Kueue -.->|multi-pod jobs| JobSet[JobSet 0.8+]
    Kueue -.->|batch workloads| AppWrapper[AppWrapper 1.1+]
    Kueue -.->|node provisioning| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler]

    %% Integration Points
    Kueue -->|admission webhooks<br/>mutate/validate| K8sAPI
    Kueue -->|aggregated API<br/>visibility server| K8sAPI
    Kueue -->|watch/patch jobs| BatchJobs[Batch Jobs]
    Kueue -.->|watch/patch| KubeflowJobs[Kubeflow Jobs]
    Kueue -.->|watch/patch| RayJobs[Ray Jobs]
    Kueue -.->|watch/patch| JobSets[JobSets]
    Kueue -.->|watch/patch| AppWrappers[AppWrappers]
    Kueue -.->|create PR| ProvisioningRequest[ProvisioningRequest CRD]
    ClusterAutoscaler -.->|watch| ProvisioningRequest

    %% MultiKueue (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|multi-cluster<br/>job dispatch| RemoteK8s[Remote K8s Clusters]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    %% (None - Kueue is standalone)

    %% Workload Types
    BatchJobs -->|managed by| Kueue
    KubeflowJobs -.->|managed by| Kueue
    RayJobs -.->|managed by| Kueue
    JobSets -.->|managed by| Kueue
    AppWrappers -.->|managed by| Kueue

